== Overview ==
This agent enable to grep log and search log files on nodes

== Usage == 
To queries all processes with rsyslog binary:
	$ mco grep FILE_NAME FILTER [-s SEARCH] [-n NUM_LINES]

* Only lines matching the filter are returned.
* The first line will match the (optional) search query
* Only NUM_LINES will be returned (defualt 100 lines)



== Installation ==
	Copy the agent, application and util directories into mcollective plugins dir (/usr/share/mcollective/plugins/mcollective/ on debian)

